the coaches - it just felt like he looked down on us.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999974039901646, \"rank\": 9.727822175838682e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alexy\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"our coaches\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the sides\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the movements\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"Alexy\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can I say this?'\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He later added: 'I tried my best to get the best result.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best result\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very surprised in the end that I broke the world record and it was a magical moment.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"a magical moment\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Last year I received 29 tests and never had a positive.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"29 tests\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From May to July, I had 21 tests, no positive.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"21 tests\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today we received a second test already.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second test\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not think there has been any impact (on me) because all the testing has been done in the normal procedure \\u2026 So it's not a big issue.'\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any impact\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"all the testing\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal procedure\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"a big issue\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WORLD RECORD!\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WORLD RECORD\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u0087Pan Zhanle breaks his own WR with a truly stunning swim in the men's 100m freestyle final.#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/4aw2myrD6L China's anti-doping agency (Chinada) has always firmly denied that their athletes have cheated, labelling the New York Times investigation: 'Extremely unfair and immoral.'\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_record\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7114328803020565e-16, \"text\": \"WR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_record\"}, {\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8486779680328097, \"rank\": 0.17828324277622234, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999998459948193, \"rank\": 8.326698509982447e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zhanle\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"a truly stunning swim\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100m freestyle\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"Chinada\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The row threatens to continue overshadowing the games however, with Australian swim coach Brett Hawke saying: 'I am angry at that [Pan's] swim.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999980205335797, \"rank\": 1.6909569344075745e-06, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brett_Hawke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brett Hawke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brett_Hawke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brett_Hawke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The row\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"that [Pan's] swim\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not win 100 freestyle by a body length on that field.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100 freestyle\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"a body length\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You just do not do it.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is not humanly possible to beat that field by a body length.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"a body length\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not real, you do not beat that field.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that field\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyle Chalmers, David Popovici, Jack Alexy, you do not beat those guys by one full body length in 100 freestyle 'That's not humanly possible okay so do not sell it to me, do not shove it down my throat.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chalmers, David\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Chalmers\"}, {\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.6793571727313876, \"rank\": 0.4633677273619562, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those guys\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"one full body length\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"100 freestyle\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"my throat\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not real.'\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Chalmers himself was only complimentary of Pan's performance and denied he had been hostile toward his rival, saying: 'Last year, I remember walking out before the final of the world championships and just he was maybe a lane next to me.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chalmers\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"Pan's performance\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"his rival\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"a lane\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He actually came up to me, and I did not know he spoke any English at that stage, and he said, \\\"Kyle, I have so much respect for you.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any English\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2887}, {\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"so much respect\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are my idol\\\".\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my idol\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Then again tonight, after the race, I congratulated him and he said, \\\"You are my idol\\\".\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3009}, {\"ngram\": \"my idol\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I look at him the same as any competitor.\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any competitor\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do everything I possibly can to win the race.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I trust that everyone's doing the same as I am and staying true to sport and the integrity of sport.\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I trust that he's done everything he possibly can to be there, and he deserves that gold medal.\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did everything I possibly could to challenge for that gold medal and be on the top of the podium.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3438}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have silver and I am just as happy with that.\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's exciting as a swimming fan and it's going to make me train harder than I have ever trained before.'\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a swimming fan\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"